          "question": "Gabriel, a homeowner, wants to fence a rectangular lot he recently bought to the landlord, since it is beside his house, there's a house wall that occupies one side of the house. He has 80 feet of fencing for the other three sides. Write the area A of the garden as a function of x only.",
